{"tid":983838,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿畀波省中起爭執　12歲仔慘遭同學擸刀捅死","createTime":"2019-01-16T09:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T10:02:56.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc371f38ad7482d155dbbe9b96abe8bde9d83665","tid":983838,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/02/023156_75ea0baeb4df3d7ba8ccddec84acda3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2F023156_75ea0baeb4df3d7ba8ccddec84acda3a.jpg&h=643e6372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賀X濤（圖）慘遭同學持刀捅死。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n湖南婁底漣源市12歲初中生賀X濤，周二（15日）中午疑不滿被13歲同班同學嚴X靈用球踢中腹部，雙方發生爭執。嚴其後持刀捅傷賀的背部、腹部等多處，後者送院後，最終搶救無效死亡。目前嚴X靈已被警方逮捕，相關部門正開展調查工作。 <br />\n<br />\n事發地點位於橋頭河鎮株木中學。據死者的賀姓姑母稱，周二正值學校期末考試，中午約12時50分休息期間，嚴X靈正在踢球，期間發生上述爭執；嚴X靈則因怒火中燒，決定回家拿刀再折返現場，將賀X濤捅死。 <br />\n<br />\n賀女表示，姪子的母親長年在廣東打工，他則一直和祖父母一同生活。事發後，其母已從廣東趕回家中。"},{"pid":"fba4b60ef98babb6bb2bcc267283a8742d08e0b7","tid":983838,"uid":2471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"終於死左..."},{"pid":"29b90b1b4cf84b083071c7cca55d712f73d340d5","tid":983838,"uid":77948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:49:26.000Z","msg":"牙X路"},{"pid":"9f894299a8200a56a46622ba501b88177c798c27","tid":983838,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母邊個踢我"},{"pid":"c1f13b04d9a7e02c4c7815ec2d3dc6536dadb4b7","tid":983838,"uid":49664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:50:39.000Z","msg":"阿雞"},{"pid":"dc63d740178683e867734e0dedeea9fb10b0ab81","tid":983838,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"喂你個波踢到我喎<br />\n你唔識閃架<br />\n靚仔咪咁寸呀你邊度架"},{"pid":"c91e62d494bc105a8b1fdffa6394f05eaca42a73","tid":983838,"uid":51172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0